Package: boostPM
Type: Package
Title: Unsupervised Tree Boosting for Learning Probability Distributions
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Naoki", "Awaya", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "nawaya@waseda.jp")
Description: Implements the unsupervised tree boosting method for learning
    probability distributions described by Awaya and Ma (2024). This initial
    development version preserves the numerical procedure of the archived
    research implementation while package structure and validation are built.
